WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.000
In order to protect these five virtues of chūshetsu, reigi, buyo, shingi, and shi-sō,

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.000
one must have a certain spirit.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:23.000
In other words, the five virtues are combined,

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:29.000
and therefore, the unfulfilled actions are all a form of apology,

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:35.000
and one must act in accordance with the conditions.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:42.000
However, in the end, the five virtues are the conditions of the heaven and earth,

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:51.000
and the conditions of the human race, and they are told to be easy to do and to protect.

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:55.000
In fact, I cannot say anything,

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:59.000
but I am very happy.

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:04.000
This is not only a text,

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:14.000
but also a sign of the path of the human race.

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:19.000
In other words, our Jikkai army,

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:24.000
in the battle of Nishin and Michiro,

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:32.000
has won the war and has made Koku-yu shine.

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:36.000
We have participated in the world war,

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:43.000
and have given our buyo to the outside world,

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:55.000
and have shown our spirit of a soldier who has lived in the wild for many years,

00:01:55.000 --> 00:02:05.000
and we believe that we are the most powerful people in the park.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:15.000
I believe that there is no one in the world who can be skilled

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:26.000
with a spirit of armor like the Japanese army.

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:37.000
The imperial army, which has a history of a glorious past,

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:48.000
is in this special room, and it must improve its skill and desire in the future.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:54.000
The existence of the imperial army, which has a history of a glorious past,

00:02:54.000 --> 00:03:03.000
is not only necessary for the development of Japan,

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:07.000
but also for the peace of the East,

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:14.000
and it is something that should guarantee the peace of the world.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:28.000
I would like to express my gratitude to the military service unit for their 50th anniversary.

